Interface KeplerGraphFrameUpdater

  • All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface KeplerGraphFrameUpdater
extends java.lang.Comparable<KeplerGraphFrameUpdater>
    An interface for updating components of a KeplerGraphFrame. Instances of this interface are used in a PriorityQueue in KeplerGraphFrame; a ClassCastException may be thrown if not a Comparable.
    Author:
    Daniel Crawl
